original: Kullberg, Tore Wilhelm, advokat, Norrköping, f. 28/9/99 i Sthlm av distr :lantmät. Martin- August K. o. Augusta Collander. G. 27 m. Birgit Andreen. Barn: Birgitta f. 28, Gunilla 31, Susanne 37. — Stud:ex. v. norra latin i Sthlm 17, jur. kand. v. Sthlmis högsk. 22. Efter tingstjg. bitr. jurist å Sthlms stads rättshj :anst. 26, förest, f. Norrköp. stads dito sed. 29. Led. av Sv:es adv:samf. sed. 37.
translated: Kullberg, Tore Wilhelm, lawyer, Norrköping, born on September 28, 1899 in Stockholm to district land surveyor Martin-August Kullberg and Augusta Collander. Married on the 27th of an undisclosed month. Spouse's name: Birgit Andreen. Children: Birgitta, born in 1928, Gunilla, born in 1931, Susanne, born in 1937. Completed upper secondary school at Norra Latin in Stockholm in 1917, obtained a law degree from Stockholm University in 1922. Started working as a junior legal counsel at Stockholm's legal aid office in 1926, became the head of Norrköping's city legal aid office in 1929. Became a member of the Swedish Bar Association in 1937.
